---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Local Real Estate News & Market Blog | Arelys Catena">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mb-12">
      <span class="text-[#C49A45] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">Market Insights & News</span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-2">Real Estate Tips & Local Updates</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-600 mt-2">Stay informed with expert advice on buying, selling, and navigating current housing market trends.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <article class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-md transition">
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="bg-[#C49A45]/10 text-[#C49A45] text-xs font-semibold px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded uppercase">Market Report</span>
            <span class="text-slate-400 text-xs">June 2026</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Summer Housing Market Trends: What Buyers & Sellers Need to Know</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">An inside look at how shifting inventory levels and interest rates are impacting local property values this season.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-2 border-t border-slate-100">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#C49A45] hover:underline">Read Full Article &rarr;</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-md transition">
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="bg-[#C49A45]/10 text-[#C49A45] text-xs font-semibold px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded uppercase">Home Staging</span>
            <span class="text-slate-400 text-xs">May 2026</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">5 Simple Upgrades That Instantly Boost Your Home’s Value</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Looking to sell soon? Discover cost-effective cosmetic updates that catch buyer attention and maximize your return on investment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-2 border-t border-slate-100">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#C49A45] hover:underline">Read Full Article &rarr;</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-md transition">
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="bg-[#C49A45]/10 text-[#C49A45] text-xs font-semibold px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded uppercase">First-Time Buyers</span>
            <span class="text-slate-400 text-xs">April 2026</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Navigating Your First Mortgage: A Step-by-Step Guide</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">From pre-approval letters to closing day costs, here is a clear roadmap to help first-time buyers feel confident through every phase.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-2 border-t border-slate-100">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#C49A45] hover:underline">Read Full Article &rarr;</span>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>